<p><b>50TH ANNIVERSARY OF THE DEATH OF THOMAS
MERTON</b>. All are invited to a day of commemoration
on Saturday, December 1, 10:00am-3:00pm at Our
Lady of the Lake Parish. <i>Thomas Merton Memorial: A
Promise of Love</i>, will feature guest speakers, a hosted lunch, recordings of 
Thomas Merton, a presentation table of his works, and a Memorial Mass at 2:00 
pm, celebrated by Father Tim Clark. Our Lady of the Lake Parish Hall, 8900 - 
35th Ave NE in Seattle; hosted by Our Lady of the Lake Parish, the International 
Thomas Merton Society, and Contemplative Outreach Northwest. RSVP requested. A 
donation of $5.00 is requested. <i>Information or to
RSVP</i>, e-mail
<a href="mailto:seattlemerton@yahoo.com?subject=Thomas Merton Memorial: A Promise of Love">seattlemerton@yahoo.com</a>.</p>


